<plot>For 15 year-old Donny, high school sucks. He's the smallest in the class and is only ever noticed when he's the butt of someone's joke. But this week it's all about to change - forever. To escape the pummeling of his life, Donny accepts the school bully's challenge to kiss Sheila, the girl of Donny's dreams, by the end of the week. Now, Donny must stumble along an absurd journey to manhood - while proving to the world that maniless is just a state of mind... and a little fake body hair.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?113809</url></doc>
